question: What are the details of the past year exam paper discussion sessions?
answer:
The sessions include:
- Engineering Mathematics I with Dr Ang Tau Keong from 8 am - 10 am
- Engineering Mathematics II with Dr Lim Yeou Jiann from 11 am - 1 pm
- Differential Equations with Dr Mohd Ariff Admon from 2 pm - 4 pm
Food is provided for the first 50 participants in each session. To join, fill out the Google form: https://forms.gle/6CuGDw9W4XNUGbYy6
For inquiries, contact Zufayri at 010-334 8656 or Aziean at 011-4018 0374.
